backgroundSecondaryColor.name: backgroundSecondaryColor
backgroundSecondaryColor.prettyName: Secondary background color (table headers, message boxes, administration boxes)

fieldGradientColor.name: fieldGradientColor
fieldGradientColor.prettyName: Field gradient color (for form elements: input, select, textarea, etc.)

headerBackgroundImage.name: headerBackgroundImage
headerBackgroundImage.prettyName: Banner (header image - the name of an image attached to the theme document)

headerBackgroundPosition.name: headerBackgroundPosition
headerBackgroundPosition.prettyName: Banner position and repeat (CSS syntax, for example: "left center no-repeat")

logoImage.name: logoImage
logoImage.prettyName: Logo (image displayed at the top left corner of the header - the name of an image attached to the theme document; if set, it has priority over the logo configured in the skin and the default logo)

pageBackgroundImage.name: pageBackgroundImage
pageBackgroundImage.prettyName: Page background image (the name of an image attached to the theme document)

pageBackgroundPosition.name: pageBackgroundPosition
pageBackgroundPosition.prettyName: Page background image position and repeat (CSS syntax, for example: "left top repeat-x")

textPrimaryColor.name: textPrimaryColor
textPrimaryColor.prettyName: Informative text color (Modified by, Created by, etc)

textSecondaryColor.name: textSecondaryColor
textSecondaryColor.prettyName: Details text color (Comments date, attachments date, etc)

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet version="1.0" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<xsl:output method="xml"/>
<xsl:template match="@*|node()"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:apply-templates select="@*|node()"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<!-- Skip fo:table-and-caption because Fop won't render tables otherwise --> <xsl:template match="fo:table-and-caption"> <xsl:apply-templates/> </xsl:template>
<!-- Ignore fo:table-caption because it is not supported --> <xsl:template match="fo:table-caption" />
<!-- Change the page dimensions to Letter --> <xsl:template match="fo:simple-page-master/@page-height"> <xsl:attribute name="page-height"> <xsl:value-of select="'11in'"/> </xsl:attribute> </xsl:template> <xsl:template match="fo:simple-page-master/@page-width"> <xsl:attribute name="page-width"> <xsl:value-of select="'8.5in'"/> </xsl:attribute> </xsl:template> <!-- Change the font to FreeSans --> <xsl:template match="fo:root/@font-family"> <xsl:attribute name="font-family"> <xsl:value-of select="'FreeSans'"/> </xsl:attribute> </xsl:template>
<!-- Change the header --> <xsl:template match="fo:static-content[@flow-name='page-header']"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:attribute name="precedence">true</xsl:attribute> <xsl:apply-templates select="@*"/> font-size="11" fill="#FFF" font-weight="bold"> <tspan><Your Department/Lab Name></tspan> </text> </svg> </fo:instream-foreign-object> </fo:block>--> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<!-- Change the footer --> <xsl:template match="fo:static-content[@flow-name='page-footer']"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:apply-templates select="@*"/> <fo:block font-size="small" space-after="0.5in" space-after.conditionality="retain" text-align="center">Page <fo:page-number/> of <fo:page-number-citation-last ref-id="x-page-sequence"/></fo:block> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<!-- Move gallery images to the end --> <!-- Step one, copy them at the end of the body --> <xsl:template match="fo:flow[@flow-name='xsl-region-body']"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:apply-templates select="@*|node()"/> <xsl:for-each select=".//*[text()='Facial dysmorphism photos:']/parent::*"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:apply-templates select="@*|node()"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:for-each> <fo:block id="last-page"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> <!-- Step two, ignore them in the body --> <xsl:template match="*[*/text()='Facial dysmorphism photos:']"> <xsl:text>See attached images</xsl:text> </xsl:template> <xsl:template match="*[text()='Facial dysmorphism photos:']"/>
<!-- Ignore some elements --> <xsl:template match="fo:block[@id='document-actions']" /> <xsl:template match="fo:block[@role='html:h1']" />
<!-- Add an ID to the whole page sequence, to be able to get the total number of pages --> <xsl:template match="fo:page-sequence"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:attribute name="id"><xsl:text>x-page-sequence</xsl:text></xsl:attribute> <xsl:apply-templates select="@*|node()"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<!-- Change the header --> <xsl:template match="fo:block[@id='xwikicontent']/fo:block[3]/fo:block-container"> <fo:table><fo:table-body><fo:table-row><fo:table-cell> <fo:block block-progression-dimension="1pt" inline-progression-dimension="1pt" content-height="1pt"> <fo:instream-foreign-object content-width="scale-to-fit" content-height="scale-to-fit" inline-progression-dimension.minimum="auto" inline-progression-dimension.maximum="100%" block-progression-dimension.minimum="auto" block-progression-dimension.maximum="700px"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" text-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="-0.5 5.5 301 80" width="150"> <title>SickKids</title> <text x="0" y="50" font-family="Impact" font-size="50" letter-spacing="3%"> <tspan fill="#8449a9">camh</tspan> </text> <rect x="0" y="55" width="300" height="30" fill="#0068b3" /> <text x="10" y="75" font-family="Arial" font-size="15" fill="#FFF" font-weight="bold"> <!--tspan><Your Department/Lab Name></tspan--> </text> </svg> </fo:instream-foreign-object> </fo:block> </fo:table-cell><fo:table-cell> <xsl:copy> <xsl:apply-templates select="@*|node()"/> </xsl:copy> </fo:table-cell></fo:table-row></fo:table-body></fo:table> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
